    dc:description "Fig. 5. Oral views. A, Hypergastromyzon humilis, CMK 10574, 31.5 mm SL; B, Hypergastromyzon abditus, MZB 17233, 37.2 mm SL; C, Hypergastromyzon sambas, MZB 17235, 32.4 mm SL." ;
